<Link id="l00968" /><CodeLine lineNumber="968"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// wavefront. When viewed from the perspective of an arbitrary workitem, this</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00969" /><CodeLine lineNumber="969"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// is 4-byte aligned.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00970" /><CodeLine lineNumber="970"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00971" /><CodeLine lineNumber="971"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Only 4-byte alignment is really needed to access anything. Transformations</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00972" /><CodeLine lineNumber="972"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// on the pointer value itself may rely on the alignment / known low bits of</span></CodeLine>
